                            </li>
                            <li>The terms and conditions of appointment of independent directors shall be open for inspection at the registered office of the company by any member during normal business hours.</li>
                            <li>The  terms  and  conditions  of  appointment  of  independent  directors  shall  also  be  posted  on  the company’s website.</li>
